<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yī tóng gēn zhǔ zǒu tiān yá 迦南281</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men yī tóng lí kāi jiā yī tóng gēn zhǔ zǒu tiān yá
 yī tóng jǔ qǐ shǒu xuān shì chuán fú yīn yī tóng jīng shòu fēng chuī yǔ dǎ
 liǎn shàng dōu yǒu lèi huā xīn lǐ gèng yǒu jǐ fēn qiān guà
 dōng lái dào běi fēng guā nǐ de mén qián shì fǒu xuě zài xià
 zhǔ ài shǐ wǒ men xīn xīn xiāng yìn zǔ gé wán quán bèi zhǔ ài róng huà
 shēng shēng wèn hòu lǐ wǒ men zhēn chéng wò wò shǒu hái yào yī tóng gēn zhǔ zǒu tiān yá.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>281</hymn_number>
</song>